# My E++ script — write in plain English!
# Mac: Cmd+Shift+B to run   |   Windows: Ctrl+Shift+B

name is called "Jim"
Age is "14"

say "Hello!"
show name
show length of name
show uppercase of name

when Age is greater than 10 then
    say "Nice to meet you, " plus name
done

show choose number between 1 and 10

